{
  "rootDuration": 216.8,
  "audioDuration": 216.6385,
  "segments": [
    {
      "scene": 1,
      "text": "同学你好，这一节我们学习七年级下册第一章，相交线与平行线。",
      "caption": "这一节学习：七年级下册第一章，相交线与平行线。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-xia-unit-1-xiang-jiao-xian-yu-ping-xing-xian/assets/sentence-segments-scene-long-stable-teacher-v1/trimmed/scene-01.wav",
      "duration": 7.253184359550562,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 7.253184359550562,
      "estimatedTiming": true
    },
    {
      "scene": 1,
      "text": "本章先看两条直线相交形成的邻补角和对顶角，再看平行线被截线截出的三类角。",
      "caption": "先学邻补角和对顶角，再学平行线中的三类角。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-xia-unit-1-xiang-jiao-xian-yu-ping-xing-xian/assets/sentence-segments-scene-long-stable-teacher-v1/trimmed/scene-01.wav",
      "duration": 9.484933393258427,
      "start": 7.253184359550562,
      "end": 16.73811775280899,
      "estimatedTiming": true
    },
    {
      "scene": 1,
      "text": "学习主线是：先找线和截线，再定角的位置，最后用相等或互补关系计算。",
      "caption": "主线：找线和截线，定角的位置，用相等或互补计算。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-xia-unit-1-xiang-jiao-xian-yu-ping-xing-xian/assets/sentence-segments-scene-long-stable-teacher-v1/trimmed/scene-01.wav",
      "duration": 8.09009024719101,
      "start": 16.73811775280899,
      "end": 24.828208,
      "estimatedTiming": true
    },
    {
      "scene": 2,
      "text": "两条直线相交，会形成四个角。判断角关系，先看是否有公共边。",
      "caption": "两条直线相交形成四个角，先看有没有公共边。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-xia-unit-1-xiang-jiao-xian-yu-ping-xing-xian/assets/sentence-segments-scene-long-stable-teacher-v1/trimmed/scene-02.wav",
      "duration": 7.068856377551021,
      "start": 25.248208,
      "end": 32.31706437755102,
      "estimatedTiming": true
    },
    {
      "scene": 2,
      "text": "有公共顶点和一条公共边，另外两边在同一直线上，这两个角是邻补角，和是一百八十度。",
      "caption": "邻补角：有公共边，另外两边在同一直线上，和为 180°。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-xia-unit-1-xiang-jiao-xian-yu-ping-xing-xian/assets/sentence-segments-scene-long-stable-teacher-v1/trimmed/scene-02.wav",
      "duration": 10.179153183673469,
      "start": 32.31706437755102,
      "end": 42.49621756122449,
      "estimatedTiming": true
    },
    {
      "scene": 2,
      "text": "面对面的两个角是对顶角，对顶角相等。",
      "caption": "对顶角：面对面的两个角，对顶角相等。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-xia-unit-1-xiang-jiao-xian-yu-ping-xing-xian/assets/sentence-segments-scene-long-stable-teacher-v1/trimmed/scene-02.wav",
      "duration": 4.524068081632653,
      "start": 42.49621756122449,
      "end": 47.02028564285715,
      "estimatedTiming": true
    },
    {
      "scene": 2,
      "text": "易混处是：邻补角不是相等，而是互补；对顶角才相等。",
      "caption": "邻补角互补，对顶角相等，别混淆。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-xia-unit-1-xiang-jiao-xian-yu-ping-xing-xian/assets/sentence-segments-scene-long-stable-teacher-v1/trimmed/scene-02.wav",
      "duration": 5.937839357142856,
      "start": 47.02028564285715,
      "end": 52.958125,
      "estimatedTiming": true
    },
    {
      "scene": 3,
      "text": "平行线问题里，要先找到截线。截线是同时穿过两条直线的那条线。",
      "caption": "平行线问题，先找到同时穿过两条直线的截线。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-xia-unit-1-xiang-jiao-xian-yu-ping-xing-xian/assets/sentence-segments-scene-long-stable-teacher-v1/trimmed/scene-03.wav",
      "duration": 7.511346870967742,
      "start": 53.378125000000004,
      "end": 60.889471870967746,
      "estimatedTiming": true
    },
    {
      "scene": 3,
      "text": "同位角在两条直线的同一侧，也在截线的同一侧，位置像上下对应。",
      "caption": "同位角：两条线同侧，截线同侧，位置上下对应。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-xia-unit-1-xiang-jiao-xian-yu-ping-xing-xian/assets/sentence-segments-scene-long-stable-teacher-v1/trimmed/scene-03.wav",
      "duration": 7.511346870967742,
      "start": 60.889471870967746,
      "end": 68.4008187419355,
      "estimatedTiming": true
    },
    {
      "scene": 3,
      "text": "内错角在两条直线之间，并且分居截线两侧。",
      "caption": "内错角：两条线之间，分居截线两侧。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-xia-unit-1-xiang-jiao-xian-yu-ping-xing-xian/assets/sentence-segments-scene-long-stable-teacher-v1/trimmed/scene-03.wav",
      "duration": 5.007564580645161,
      "start": 68.4008187419355,
      "end": 73.40838332258066,
      "estimatedTiming": true
    },
    {
      "scene": 3,
      "text": "同旁内角也在两条直线之间，但它们在截线同一侧。",
      "caption": "同旁内角：两条线之间，在截线同一侧。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-xia-unit-1-xiang-jiao-xian-yu-ping-xing-xian/assets/sentence-segments-scene-long-stable-teacher-v1/trimmed/scene-03.wav",
      "duration": 5.842158677419334,
      "start": 73.40838332258066,
      "end": 79.250542,
      "estimatedTiming": true
    },
    {
      "scene": 4,
      "text": "如果两直线平行，那么同位角相等，内错角相等，同旁内角互补。",
      "caption": "两直线平行：同位角相等，内错角相等，同旁内角互补。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-xia-unit-1-xiang-jiao-xian-yu-ping-xing-xian/assets/sentence-segments-scene-long-stable-teacher-v1/trimmed/scene-04.wav",
      "duration": 6.690034278350515,
      "start": 79.670542,
      "end": 86.3605762783505,
      "estimatedTiming": true
    },
    {
      "scene": 4,
      "text": "反过来，如果同位角相等，或者内错角相等，就可以判定两条直线平行。",
      "caption": "同位角或内错角相等，可以判定两直线平行。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-xia-unit-1-xiang-jiao-xian-yu-ping-xing-xian/assets/sentence-segments-scene-long-stable-teacher-v1/trimmed/scene-04.wav",
      "duration": 7.492838391752577,
      "start": 86.3605762783505,
      "end": 93.85341467010308,
      "estimatedTiming": true
    },
    {
      "scene": 4,
      "text": "如果同旁内角互补，也可以判定两条直线平行。",
      "caption": "同旁内角互补，也可以判定两直线平行。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-xia-unit-1-xiang-jiao-xian-yu-ping-xing-xian/assets/sentence-segments-scene-long-stable-teacher-v1/trimmed/scene-04.wav",
      "duration": 5.084426051546392,
      "start": 93.85341467010308,
      "end": 98.93784072164947,
      "estimatedTiming": true
    },
    {
      "scene": 4,
      "text": "做题时先判断题目给的是平行还是角度关系，方向不要用反。",
      "caption": "先看题目给的是“平行”还是“角度关系”。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-xia-unit-1-xiang-jiao-xian-yu-ping-xing-xian/assets/sentence-segments-scene-long-stable-teacher-v1/trimmed/scene-04.wav",
      "duration": 6.690034278350524,
      "start": 98.93784072164947,
      "end": 105.62787499999999,
      "estimatedTiming": true
    },
    {
      "scene": 5,
      "text": "看例题一：两条直线相交，已知其中一个角为五十八度，求它的邻补角和对顶角。",
      "caption": "例题一：已知一个角 58°，求邻补角和对顶角。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-xia-unit-1-xiang-jiao-xian-yu-ping-xing-xian/assets/sentence-segments-scene-long-stable-teacher-v1/trimmed/scene-05.wav",
      "duration": 8.35729585046729,
      "start": 106.04787499999999,
      "end": 114.40517085046729,
      "estimatedTiming": true
    },
    {
      "scene": 5,
      "text": "邻补角与已知角组成平角，所以邻补角等于一百八十度减五十八度，等于一百二十二度。",
      "caption": "邻补角 = 180° - 58° = 122°。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-xia-unit-1-xiang-jiao-xian-yu-ping-xing-xian/assets/sentence-segments-scene-long-stable-teacher-v1/trimmed/scene-05.wav",
      "duration": 9.4019578317757,
      "start": 114.40517085046729,
      "end": 123.80712868224299,
      "estimatedTiming": true
    },
    {
      "scene": 5,
      "text": "对顶角与已知角相等，所以对顶角等于五十八度。",
      "caption": "对顶角与已知角相等，所以是 58°。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-xia-unit-1-xiang-jiao-xian-yu-ping-xing-xian/assets/sentence-segments-scene-long-stable-teacher-v1/trimmed/scene-05.wav",
      "duration": 5.223309906542055,
      "start": 123.80712868224299,
      "end": 129.03043858878505,
      "estimatedTiming": true
    },
    {
      "scene": 5,
      "text": "答案是：邻补角一百二十二度，对顶角五十八度。",
      "caption": "答案：邻补角 122°，对顶角 58°。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-xia-unit-1-xiang-jiao-xian-yu-ping-xing-xian/assets/sentence-segments-scene-long-stable-teacher-v1/trimmed/scene-05.wav",
      "duration": 4.96214441121495,
      "start": 129.03043858878505,
      "end": 133.992583,
      "estimatedTiming": true
    },
    {
      "scene": 6,
      "text": "看例题二：直线 a 平行于 b，被截线 c 所截，在点 A 处有一个内角是六十八度。",
      "caption": "例题二：a ∥ b，截线 c 所截，已知 ∠4 = 68°。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-xia-unit-1-xiang-jiao-xian-yu-ping-xing-xian/assets/sentence-segments-scene-long-stable-teacher-v1/trimmed/scene-06.wav",
      "duration": 8.696905416000002,
      "start": 134.41258299999998,
      "end": 143.10948841599998,
      "estimatedTiming": true
    },
    {
      "scene": 6,
      "text": "与角四同位的角是角八，因为两直线平行，所以角八也等于六十八度。",
      "caption": "同位角相等：∠8 = ∠4 = 68°。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-xia-unit-1-xiang-jiao-xian-yu-ping-xing-xian/assets/sentence-segments-scene-long-stable-teacher-v1/trimmed/scene-06.wav",
      "duration": 7.855269408,
      "start": 143.10948841599998,
      "end": 150.96475782399997,
      "estimatedTiming": true
    },
    {
      "scene": 6,
      "text": "与角四同旁内的角是角六，它们互补，所以角六等于一百八十度减六十八度，也就是一百一十二度。",
      "caption": "同旁内角互补：∠6 = 180° - 68° = 112°。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-xia-unit-1-xiang-jiao-xian-yu-ping-xing-xian/assets/sentence-segments-scene-long-stable-teacher-v1/trimmed/scene-06.wav",
      "duration": 11.221813440000002,
      "start": 150.96475782399997,
      "end": 162.18657126399998,
      "estimatedTiming": true
    },
    {
      "scene": 6,
      "text": "答案是：同位角角八为六十八度，同旁内角角六为一百一十二度。",
      "caption": "答案：∠8 = 68°，∠6 = 112°。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-xia-unit-1-xiang-jiao-xian-yu-ping-xing-xian/assets/sentence-segments-scene-long-stable-teacher-v1/trimmed/scene-06.wav",
      "duration": 7.2941787360000205,
      "start": 162.18657126399998,
      "end": 169.48075,
      "estimatedTiming": true
    },
    {
      "scene": 7,
      "text": "本章最容易错的地方有三个。第一，没先找截线，就急着判断角名。",
      "caption": "易错点 1：没先找截线就判断角名。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-xia-unit-1-xiang-jiao-xian-yu-ping-xing-xian/assets/sentence-segments-scene-long-stable-teacher-v1/trimmed/scene-07.wav",
      "duration": 7.674748739726027,
      "start": 169.90075,
      "end": 177.57549873972602,
      "estimatedTiming": true
    },
    {
      "scene": 7,
      "text": "第二，把同旁内角误认为相等；第三，知道要减一百八十度，却漏写角度单位。",
      "caption": "易错点 2：把同旁内角误认为相等；易错点 3：漏写单位。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-xia-unit-1-xiang-jiao-xian-yu-ping-xing-xian/assets/sentence-segments-scene-long-stable-teacher-v1/trimmed/scene-07.wav",
      "duration": 8.855479315068493,
      "start": 177.57549873972602,
      "end": 186.4309780547945,
      "estimatedTiming": true
    },
    {
      "scene": 7,
      "text": "每次做题按三步来：找截线，定位置，用关系。",
      "caption": "三步：找截线，定位置，用关系。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-xia-unit-1-xiang-jiao-xian-yu-ping-xing-xian/assets/sentence-segments-scene-long-stable-teacher-v1/trimmed/scene-07.wav",
      "duration": 5.018104945205465,
      "start": 186.4309780547945,
      "end": 191.44908299999997,
      "estimatedTiming": true
    },
    {
      "scene": 8,
      "text": "最后总结：相交线看邻补和对顶，平行线看同位、内错和同旁内。",
      "caption": "相交线看邻补和对顶，平行线看三类角。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-xia-unit-1-xiang-jiao-xian-yu-ping-xing-xian/assets/sentence-segments-scene-long-stable-teacher-v1/trimmed/scene-08.wav",
      "duration": 6.579510164835164,
      "start": 191.86908299999996,
      "end": 198.44859316483513,
      "estimatedTiming": true
    },
    {
      "scene": 8,
      "text": "学完这一章，你要能识别角关系，会用相等和互补求角，也能根据角关系判定平行。",
      "caption": "会识别角关系，会用相等和互补求角，也能判定平行。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-xia-unit-1-xiang-jiao-xian-yu-ping-xing-xian/assets/sentence-segments-scene-long-stable-teacher-v1/trimmed/scene-08.wav",
      "duration": 8.684953417582419,
      "start": 198.44859316483513,
      "end": 207.13354658241755,
      "estimatedTiming": true
    },
    {
      "scene": 8,
      "text": "现在回到软件里完成第一章单元小测，检查自己能不能把图形中的关系读出来。",
      "caption": "回到软件里完成第一章单元小测。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-xia-unit-1-xiang-jiao-xian-yu-ping-xing-xian/assets/sentence-segments-scene-long-stable-teacher-v1/trimmed/scene-08.wav",
      "duration": 8.68495341758242,
      "start": 207.13354658241755,
      "end": 215.81849999999997,
      "estimatedTiming": true
    }
  ],
